144
00:08:17,810 --> 00:08:19,730
to survive in nature.

145
00:08:21,050 --> 00:08:21,810
So,

146
00:08:22,930 --> 00:08:23,810
Lele, do you want to

147
00:08:23,810 --> 00:08:25,170
be like butterflies

148
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:27,400
to protect yourself

149
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:28,930
as well as others,

150
00:08:29,130 --> 00:08:30,200
