197
00:11:21,450 --> 00:11:22,520
I don't know.

198
00:11:24,330 --> 00:11:25,330
I have surgeries.

199
00:11:54,330 --> 00:11:55,250
Well, Mingming,

200
00:11:55,970 --> 00:11:56,490
didn't you say

201
00:11:56,490 --> 00:11:57,920
you had contacted people here?

202
