218
00:13:25,210 --> 00:13:26,040
Xiong Fei,

219
00:13:26,400 --> 00:13:27,680
get up from the south.

220
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:29,330
There are more props

221
00:13:29,640 --> 00:13:30,610
