will be more dynamic.

235
00:14:19,680 --> 00:14:20,880
Are you going back to town?

236
00:14:21,570 --> 00:14:22,370
Sure.

237
00:14:23,130 --> 00:14:24,730
But I have a truckload of goods...

238
00:14:28,330 --> 00:14:29,970
