268
00:16:22,250 --> 00:16:23,330
Hang in there.

269
00:16:23,330 --> 00:16:24,490
I'm coming to save you now.

270
00:16:26,040 --> 00:16:27,800
Can you hear me, sir?

271
00:16:30,920 --> 00:16:31,490
